WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:40.120
1. Apply base gel to the nails and cure.

00:00:42.680 --> 00:00:59.720
2. Apply a small amount of clear gel on the brush and add it over the nails.

00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:13.040
3. Apply gel on the brush and put some glitter on it then add it over the nails.

00:01:13.040 --> 00:01:15.040
Tip : You can use base gel instead of clear gel.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:25.920
4. Densely fill the glitter from the bottom part and create gradient using the powder glitter.

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:35.120
5. Buff the nails to do an overlay with clear gel.

00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:44.720
Do an overlay with clear gel as the glitter makes the nail surface uneven.

00:01:44.720 --> 00:02:05.120
Add the clear gel in the middle to 
match the cuticle line and do an overlay with clear gel by dragging it down to the bottom using the brush.

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:17.440
[Before overlay / After overlay]

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:31.120
6. Apply top gel to the nails and remove any sticky residue.

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:38.960
[Glitter powder french nail art]

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:54.800
1.Apply base gel or clear gel on the colored nails and densely sprinkle the glitter powder over the nails.

00:02:57.920 --> 00:03:04.160
Tip: It makes the nail look clear by applying one coat of color.

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:09.440
Wash the brush using a kitchen towel and trim lines with the brush.

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:17.760
2. Do an overlay with base gel to cover the glitter.

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:27.200
3. Apply top gel and remove any sticky residue.

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:33.760
[Glitter dot nail art]

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:50.720
1. After applying a full coat of color, add clear gel or base gel and put glitter dots on the nails.

00:03:51.760 --> 00:04:11.680
Tip: For the glitter dots, you can easily pick them up with a wood stick or a line brush.

00:04:14.320 --> 00:04:32.400
2.Do an overlay with clear gel to cover the glitter.

00:04:35.760 --> 00:04:51.200
3.Apply top gel and remove any sticky residue.

